column5: Any reports on Sabaskong/Morson fishing? Water temp? Water level appears to be a bit higher than last year at this time, I think? Crappie? Thanks, Bill
Water temps around 76 before the cold front. We've been catching lots of crappies but not in the elbow.
Bill, When you going up to Young's? We'll be at Mylie's the 6th to the 12th. Jared, hope to stop by and see you this trip. Marv

I'll be at Young's starting Sep. 21, guess we won't be running into each other, again. Shoot us a report when you get back, and mark an "X" on the side of your boat at the hot spots! Friends of mine will be at Jared's the same time as I am at Young's, hope to meet up with them for a day or so. Good luck, Bill
Bill,I will be at Red Wing the 13th - 21st. Guess we will not hook up again also.Jared,If not the elbow, are you catching them on the brush piles or up by Thompson Creeek?Brett
"Like ships passing in the night".....er, on the road. Good luck, Bill
